<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3629.1.1>
    bibo:endPage "106" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2013-03-18" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "3629" ;
    dc:creator "Blank, Stephan M.; Shinohara, Akihiko; Altenhofer, Ewald" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "<strong> The Eurasian species of <em> Xyela </ em> (Hymenoptera, Xyelidae): taxonomy, host plants and distribution </ strong>" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261372>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261380>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261388>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261352>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261350>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261368>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261348> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261372>
    dc:description "FIGURES 42–65. Color pattern of head of Xyela species: X. curva group, X. rasnitsyni group, X. julii group (part). Legend: HT—holotype; NT—neotype; PT—paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5261372/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261380>
    dc:description "FIGURES 105–120. Ovipositor sheaths of Xyela species. All figures at same scale. Legend: HT—holotype; NT—neotype; PT—paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5261380/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261388>
    dc:description "FIGURES 136–145. Penis valves of Xyela species: X. curva group, X. julii group (part). Figs 138–139 and 141 reproduced from Blank et al. (2005)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5261388/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261352>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Records of Xyela graeca (553 specimens from 53 collection sites) and natural distribution of the host plant, Pinus nigra (solid line, combined from Meusel et al. 1965 and Barbéro et al. 1998)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5261352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261350>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Emergence phenology of imagines of Xyela curva, X. graeca and X. menelaus under laboratory conditions between 24.3. (= day 1) and 19.4.1999 (= day 25). Rearing data from two almost syntopic samples (Z42A/98, Z42B/98) taken from Pinus nigra pallasiana in southern Turkey in 1998." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5261350/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261368>
    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Barcoding analysis of Xyela species. The tree is primarily based on specimens for which COI sequences longer than 600 bp and including less than three ambigous nucleotides could be obtained. Some shorter sequences have been added to associate sexes or larvae with imagines. Each specimen is labelled as follows: “Xyela ...”—species name; “DEIGISHym ...”—unique identification number of specimen in DEI collection; “Male / Female”—sex, larva if no sex is indicated; e.g., “661” / “603” / “658” ...—base pairs [bp] sequence length; “[0n] / [1n] / [2n]”—0–2 ambiguous nucleotides included in sequence; e.g., “Austria, Karnten [= Kärnten, Carinthia]”—country and province of origin of specimen; “BOLD: ...”—globally unique identifier (GUID). The label “Xyela 005 P. sabiniana sp.” refers to larvae obtained from Pinus sabiniana which here are identified as X. bakeri." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5261368/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5261348>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Records of Xyela altenhoferi (12 specimens from 1 collection site) and natural distribution of the host plant, Pinus halepensis (solid line, according to Barbéro et al. 1998). “B?” and “H?” denote additional collection sites of similar, unidentified Xyela specimens collected close to or reared from P. brutia or P. halepensis (see text)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5261348/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

